title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 22 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: Biden makes no sense at town hall, hailed as a great statesman. Biden has lost his faculties. Clay reports on the mask mandate in L.A. Biden lies about the covid vaccine, says you won't get covid if you get the vaccination. Throwdown Thursday: Seniors rebel against Clay's suggestion that we have a 65-year-old age limit for presidents. Childlike Biden says massive spending will reduce inflation.
